<p><strong>Skiing Journal</strong></p>
<p> Inspired by my friend <a href="https://www.winstonhsiao.com/" target="_blank">Winston</a>, I wanted to start writing about my ski adventures. I learned how to ski as a kid in the Poconos and the Catskills, but I didn't start improving until we started visting Vermont frequently when I was in Middle School and High School. My appreciation for skiing and pushing me out of my comfort zone grew tremendously as I finished college, and it's no longer something I can live without.</p>

